name: Quinjet
description: Combining the technological prowess of Wakandan engineering and Stark Industries, Quinjets have served both the Avengers and S.H.I.E.L.D. operatives as a rapid-response vehicle able to carry them where a crisis mounts. Agile in the air and the vacuum of space and resistant to the pressure of deep water operations, Quinjets are a crucial part of how the Earth's mightiest heroes and covert teams can arrive wherever they are needed most.
